'''Edgefields-on-Varonat''' was a city on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Varonat/Legends|Varonat]]. Founded alongside [[Tropis-on-Varonat]] circa [[250 BBY/Legends|250 BBY]]<ref>"Galactic Gazetteer: Hoth and the Greater Javin" claims the city was settled 250 years before the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].</ref> by [[Human/Legends|Humans]] from [[Salliche/Legends|Salliche]], the city's population eventually grew to around several thousand individuals.

